<h2>🧐 White chocolate cannabis cake recipe</h2>
&nbsp;

I'd tell you that this recipe is for the whole family, but you know I would lie to you, so if you have kids at home... <em>keep it away from their reach, because it's tempting!</em> Of course, you can make the same recipe without using cannabis, if you want to make it for them.

&nbsp;

What are we gonna need?

&nbsp;
<div class="pfgreen">
<ul>
 	<li>A packet of biscuits</li>
 	<li>120 grams of butter</li>
 	<li>2 sachets of curd</li>
 	<li>200 grams of white chocolate</li>
 	<li>250 grams of milk</li>
 	<li>200 grams of cream</li>
</ul>
</div>
&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_21312" align="aligncenter" width="575"]<img class="wp-image-21312 size-full" title=" Ingredients white chocolate cake with cannabis" src="https://pevgrow.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/chocolate-blanco-tarta-ingredientes.jpg" alt=" Ingredients white chocolate cake with cannabis" width="575" height="200" /> Ingredients white chocolate cake with cannabis[/caption]

&nbsp;

Once you have all the kitchen stuff, taking the steps as follows:

&nbsp;

<strong><em>First:</em></strong> we'll make the pie base. To do this, crush the biscuits and mix them with the butter that we have previously melted (the easiest way is to do it in the microwave). Mix well and make a kind of pasta which later we will put in the mold where we want to make the cake. Then, We’ll put it in the fridge.

&nbsp;

[caption id="attachment_21318" align="aligncenter" width="575"]<img class="wp-image-21318 size-full" title="We'll make the pie base" src="https://pevgrow.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/chocolate-blanco-tarta-paso-01.jpg" alt="We'll make the pie base" width="575" height="200" /> We'll make the pie base[/caption]

&nbsp;

